Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:400;line-height:1.3;margin:0 auto;padding:0;text-align:left;text-decoration:none">Overnightglasses.com</a></li><li style="color:#666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;line-height:22px">Exclusive Access to certain brand name frames available for ONG Elite club members only</li><li style="color:#666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;line-height:22px">Possibility to share your exclusive discount with friends and family</li><li style="color:#666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;line-height:22px">Cash Rebate on each purchase made by you or your friends and family on ONG website using your unique discount code. The amount of the rebate will be visible when accessing your personal account on overnight glasses website. You can use this rebate for future purchases on ONG or you can cash it*.</li></ul><p style="Margin:0;Margin-bottom:10px;color:#666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:22px;margin:0;margin-bottom:10px;padding:0;text-align:left">Our goal at <a href="https://www.overnightglasses.com/" style="Margin:0;color:#A49063;cursor:pointer;font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:400;line-height:1.3;margin:0 auto;padding:0;text-align:left;text-decoration:none">Overnightglasses.com</a> is to provide our customer with the best available pair of glasses in record time for the most competitive price</p><div class="thank-you-text"><p style="Margin:0;Margin-bottom:10px;color:#666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:22px;margin:0;margin-bottom:10px;padding:0;text-align:left"><span style="color:#333;font-weight:700">Thank you</span> again<br>for being a great customer,<br>Michael,<br>Overnight Glasses Club Management.<br></p><p class="little-grey-text" style="Margin:0;Margin-bottom:10px;color:#7F7F7F;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:15px;font-weight:400;line-height:22px;margin:0;margin-bottom:10px;padding:0;text-align:left">*certain restrictions apply</p></div><table class="button large seconda